Hence, we found Earl.
Who is this guy anyways and why does he charge only $5.99 per sandwich?
Anyways since I was starving, I ordered the Jamaican Jerk Chicken sandwich and the Hawaiian BBQ and both did not disappoint.
Their bread is so soft and warm, the chicken is hot and tender, the sauce just exploded in my mouth.
