A Few Tips before going to Earl's  1.
Go to the Miracle Mile Information Booth and ask for a Coupon Book.
Inside you will find a 10% OFF coupon (entire purchase).
If they asked how did you hear about the coupon, let them know you heard it from Southwest.
Lines could get long after 12 p.m, but they're very efficient and they move insanely fast.
Open 24hrs.
