The place is located inside the Planet Hollywood across from the sports book.
It's open 24/7 for all you lovely belligerent and drunk, 5 inch heels in hand meaning blackened Hobbit feet, crusted yack on chin folks.
The Earl just might be your savior.
For a measly $5-6, you can get a nice, freshly made and toasted sandwich.
There are many options to choose from such as the classic club to the Hawaiian bbq.
