I've been here twice now and Earl of Sandwich has demonstrated consistency in terms of quality hot sandwiches and customer service.
I've had the Earl's Club and the Full Montagu.
The sandwiches are cut in half and when you pull them apart, a string of cheese follows--YUM!
The club sandwich had turkey, bacon, swiss cheese, tomatoes, lettuce, and some sort of sauce.
The Montagu sandwich had swiss and cheddar cheese, turkey, roast beef, lettuce, tomatoes, and Earl's mustard sauce!
