Oh and that potato salad was  oh so good.
The bf got The Original which he actually enjoyed.
He said it was a lot better than last time but could've used more au jus.
All in all, we spent under 18 bucks, including water, and was fully satisfied with the meal.
Would I say this is the best tuna sandwich I've ever had?
Probably not.
But the best tuna sandwich I've had in the strip so far?
Absolutely!

