The sandwiches are always always, ahem, always amazing.
Packed with flavor, fresh veggies and meats and melted cheese between two toasted slices of bread, it's quality food that fills your tummy and leaves you happy and satisfied.
They do simple so well it's admirable.
Oh and try the soup, it's clutch.

