Quick tips first though!
There is a parking structure that enters into the rear of the Miracle Mile Shops.
Earl of Sandwich is located near the entrance of the casino via Las Vegas Blvd.
If you're taking the walkway, the shop is on the first floor.
There is no direct elevator down to the first floor from the second floor shops!
Use the escalator.
