The line is always long but it passes fast.
You order at the register and they give you a receipt and a buzzer (is that what those are called?
) for your food.
You can then pick up drinks, chips, or other small items, such as fruit cups and parfaits, on the way to the next register, where you give them your receipt and pay.
Find a table and when your food is ready, the buzzer will light up and vibrate.
Get your food and enjoy!

